listing.access:
Very compact full containing ground floor garden studio.
Kitchen with microwave, stove and fridge. 
Bathroom with thermostat shower. 
Central heating with own thermostat. 
TV and WiFi. 
Outdoor patio. 
Comfortable bed. 
Quiet at backyard.
Modern studio in historic building.
listing.description: Unique studio at unique location. Right in the green and quiet part of the city centre with public transport, shops, restaurants, sights and attractions just around the corner. Comfortable and convenient, modern compact space for 1-2 people.
listing.house_rules:
No smoking - except for at patio use ashtray
No bicycles parking
No invitees - 24/7 day and night
No hard drugs
No check in after midnight
Do your dishes before check out
listing.neighborhood_overview: The neighborhood is relatively green and quiet but very central and with a high level of amenities and facilities like opera, theatre, cinema, cafés, restaurants, transport, shops, museums and attractions.
listing.notes:
Ground floor - convenient with luggage
Minimum stay 4 nights - 2 or 3 nights possible only in between standing bookings with only 2 or 3 nights left
Small studio - not for people in need of a lot of space
Only booked people can stay here 24/7

listing.public_address: H Nieuwe Herengracht, Amsterdam, NH 1011 RN, Netherlands
listing.space:
Very central location - Next to the National Opera, Hermitage museum, Waterloo and Rembrandt plaza
Quiet east side of city centre - Near Plantage, Hortus and Zoo 
Metro and tram at 3 minutes - Waterloo metro to / from CS 5 minutes, just 2 stops
Supermarket at 5 minutes - Albert Heijn at Jodenbreestraat, Marqt at Herengracht 
Museums at 5 minutes - Hermitage, Rembrandthouse, Willet Holthuysen canal museum, Jewish Historic Museum. 
Shops at 5 minutes - Utrechtse straat, Waterloo flea market, St Antonie Breest.
listing.summary: Unique studio at unique location. Right in the green and quiet part of the city centre with public transport, shops, restaurants, sights and attractions just around the corner. Comfortable and convenient, modern compact space for 1-2 people.
listing.transit:
TO CENTRAL STATION 
Train from Airport to Central station - 15 mins. 
(Tram 26/bus 37 from P+R Zeeburg I+II (car park) to Central station - 10 mins. ) 
TO WATERLOO
Tram 9/ 14 (5 stops Dam-Spui-Munt-Rembrandt-Waterloo) or metro (Any line) stops Nieuwmarkt-Waterloo) from Central Station to Waterlooplein - 10 mins. 
TO ACCOMMODATION 
The apartment is around the block from Waterlooplein - a 3 minutes walk.

review.comments:
We had a an excellent stay at Conny's flat. The organiation was very easy because she replied super fast. 
The flat is very cozy and and has everything. The area is calm and very close to the center. I would book it again.
